snippet.title: Grey Eminence - Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
A new era is dawning for the historical grand strategy genre!

Watch the first official alpha gameplay preview of Grey Eminence, which will soon be launching into closed alpha for supporters on Patreon: https://patreon.com/nestinars

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1858700/Grey_Eminence/
Subscribe to our newsletter: https://nestinars.com/#subscribe
_____________________________________________________________

Reddit: https://reddit.com/r/greyeminence
Discord: https://discord.gg/greyeminence
Facebook: https://facebook.com/nestinars
Twitter: https://twitter.com/nestinars
_____________________________________________________________

Narration by Colin Cassidy
Music by Daniel Ketchum
